Package: SmarterScotland
Type: Package
Title: Source Public Data from statistics.gov.scot
Version: 0.0.09
Date: 2016-02-03
Authors@R: person("Konrad", "Zdeb", email = "konrad.zdeb@me.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package sources the publicly available data life outcomes, 
  demographic and administrative  data from the ScotStat portal for selected indicators, 
  geographies and time periods. In addition the package offers basic visualisation and 
  analytical functionalities.
